flowchart TD
    A[CRM: Create Lead] --> B[Prepare Quotation]
    B --> C{Client Accepts?}
    C -- No --> Z[Close as Lost]
    C -- Yes --> D[Create Project Record<br/>Contract Value, Budget, Project Manager assigned]

    D --> E[Client pays Mobilization Advance]
    E --> F[Journal: Dr Bank / Cr Client Advances<br/>No revenue recognized yet]

    D --> G[Project Manager submits<br/>Periodic Completion Assessment]
    G --> H[Accountant reviews and approves assessment]
    H --> I[System posts Revenue Recognition Journal<br/>Dr Contract Assets-WIP / Cr Revenue<br/>amount = Contract Value x percent complete, less revenue already recognized]

    I --> J[Accountant raises Milestone Invoice]
    J --> K[System posts Invoice Journal<br/>Dr Accounts Receivable<br/>Cr Contract Assets-WIP up to recognized revenue<br/>Cr Client Advances for any excess billed<br/>Cr VAT / NHIL / GETFund Output]

    K --> L[Client makes Payment against Invoice]
    L --> M[Journal: Dr Bank / Cr Accounts Receivable]

    F --> N[Financial Reports auto-update:<br/>Trial Balance, Income Statement, Statement of Financial Position]
    I --> N
    M --> N

    N --> O[Executive Dashboard reflects<br/>Cash Position, Revenue, Project Profitability]
